-It's very smart.
-Thank you.

40:36.301 --> 40:38.067
-And well-written.
-I wrote it myself.

40:38.069 --> 40:40.270
-And a total bore.
-There was a ghostwriter.

40:40.272 --> 40:42.739
This is a book that screams,
